A pacman map I made. The T's have knifes and nades, while the CT's start with a usp (with only one mag). There really isn't a point to this, as I couldn't think of a way to end it.

If you have any thoughts on how you could make this better, feel free to leave a comment below, and I'll try to do it.

<3 Partyhard Porygon
